Jenkins backup is a solution for keeping the backup of critical configuration settings related to Jenkins1. Jenkins has a backup plugin that 
can be used to backup1. One of the backup plugins is Jenkins Thin Backup, which backs up all the data based on your schedule and handles the 
backup retention. To make Jenkins backup, you must locate the Jenkins home folder,which is hidden by default. You can also backup the jobs 
folder separately, which contains all the details of each job.	
	


